title: Cross sections of N-14 interaction with Nb-93 at 78 and 118 MeV

x4freetext: Cross sections of N-14 interaction with Nb-93 at
78 and 118 MeV
Metallic foil of niobium.
Thickness - 1 mg/cm2, approximately the
target was disposed inside Faraday`s cup.
Beam current was 1 particle nano-Ampere,
approximately.
To produce 78 MeV beam.
+6 N-14 ions.
